        "1654cb88-d978-4d7b-9570-548c2b5d6c4f": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Made in Italy",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>Our <strong>Breton Shirts</strong> are crafted just a few kilometers from <strong>Venice</strong>, in a region known for its rich artisanal heritage and its role in producing garments for the world’s top <strong>high-fashion brands</strong>.</p><p>Each piece is meticulously made from <strong>premium cotton</strong>, sourced from a renowned Italian mill in <strong>Biella</strong>, celebrated for its exceptional quality, softness, and breathability—perfect for year-round comfort.</p><p>We collaborate with a <strong>small, family-run workshop</strong>, fostering a partnership built on <strong>trust, craftsmanship, and a passion for quality</strong>—values that define every garment we create.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "47bfb772-5b4f-4198-802a-23f7ca18048d": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Handmade Embroidery",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>Our Marinières are hand embroidered with needle and thread, making each one unique. </p><p>Each pieces is also hand numbered, from 1 to 99.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_weyDdD": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Fit",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>The oversized fit, the dropped sleeves and wide boat neck are hallmarks of our design. Taken together, they represent a unique, modern and fashionable update of this classic look, making them perfect for every outfit.<br/></p><p>Available from S to L. We recommend ordering your normal size. Consult our sizing chart for the correct measurements. If you prefer a slimmer fit, order a size down. If you are unsure or need some advice, send us a message and we will be happy to help.<br/><br/>The model in the photo is 189 cm tall and wears size L.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "e9567a30-a8a4-47b3-ac6b-dd845b2d3a7c": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Fabric & Care",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>We craft our <strong>Breton Shirts</strong> in <strong>Italy</strong> using a <strong>manual loom</strong>, ensuring each piece is meticulously knitted rather than cut from pre-printed fabric. Every sweater is made by skilled artisans, using over <strong>2.5 kilometers of raw yarn</strong>, preserving the authenticity of traditional craftsmanship.</p><p>To keep your <strong>Breton Shirt</strong> looking its best, <strong>hand wash or machine wash at 30°C</strong>, then <strong>hang to dry</strong>. If needed, <strong>iron inside out</strong> or use <strong>steam</strong> to remove creases.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "d808420e-8e92-4566-9948-7577a69f3f77": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Handmade Embroidery",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>Our Marinières are hand embroidered with needle and thread, making each one unique. </p><p>Each pieces is also hand numbered, from 1 to 99.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_DTxwDD": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>Shipping is free.</p><p>Once your Marinière is dispatched, you'll receive an email with tracking details. We ship all over the world. And if you’re based in the EU, we will be sending your items directly from Italy so that you won’t incur additional customs fees.</p><p>If for any reason you wanted to return your Marinière, we accept returns within 14 days of delivery as long as the Marinièere is in perfect condition.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
